{"tid":1533712,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"真心，你覺得圍狗屋有無用","createTime":"2019-09-02T19:42:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T01:43:10.000Z","uid":122031,"like":4,"dislike":56,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2efd3bf28b7eba2fde94cfb68c7ec8e006bb603f","tid":1533712,"uid":122031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T19:42:39.000Z","msg":"首先，唔係分化撚 我只係想問下大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地覺得圍狗屋有咩作用 雖然話係撚狗等佢出黎就走 <br />\n<br />\n但每次撚狗個日點都有人被捉 仲要暴力對待<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇到我每次都好撚心痛 又覺得好唔抵 好無力 所以先想問下大家意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有用 繼續圍<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />另諗方法啦！"},{"pid":"bcf47729357ab05c088aa7d6ba31eeee646a8178","tid":1533712,"uid":250744,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T19:49:06.000Z","msg":"有火魔法就有用"},{"pid":"6d5dcec03d49b503c16cff26e81766a139012f4a","tid":1533712,"uid":122031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bcf47729357ab05c088aa7d6ba31eeee646a8178","tid":1533712,"uid":250744,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T19:49:06.000Z","msg":"有火魔法就有用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T19:51:00.000Z","msg":"但係其實今晚無諗住開波 咁就拉左十幾個<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8acb42d2fbd3f4fe68eceb40f8464e903dbae8f2","tid":1533712,"uid":122031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T19:51:29.000Z","msg":"十連1"},{"pid":"6ba6fba796aa4a144d0fb5fd16376f2a18a66b7a","tid":1533712,"uid":122031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T19:51:39.000Z","msg":"十連2"},{"pid":"256c82bab1d4c5cad5ae5b7c6206edebb2663ccf","tid":1533712,"uid":122031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T19:51:53.000Z","msg":"十連3"},{"pid":"fe